log log.lammps

units 			metal
boundary 		p p p 
atom_style 		full
neigh_modify    delay 5 every 5 check yes
pair_style 		eam/fs 

read_data	min.data
pair_coeff 		* * AgX1.0.eam.alloy  Ag

group Boost id 501
group NonBoost subtract all Boost

fix 1 all langevin 600.0 600.0 1000.0 305363
fix 2 all nve
compute event all event/displace 1.2
fix diffusion Boost hyper/global 3.32 0.3 0.30 600
fix 3 all momentum 1 linear 1 1 1 angular
hyper 500000 100 diffusion event